      About this item

      • Comfortable Support: Expertly engineered with a high-density foam and spring system that delivers the perfect balance of plush softness and supportive structurethe integrated spring system provides lasting resilience and extended durability, while the memory foam delivers a sensation of cloud-like comfort. Designed for ultimate relaxation, the generous 28" seat depth, elevated back cushion and arcuate armrests create an inviting lounging oasis, while the spacious 58" chaise lounge offers ample room to stretch out. Thoughtfully incorporated ergonomic features ensure ideal support for prolonged sitting or reclining
      • Fully Modular Design: This modular sofa offers ultimate flexibility with a total width of 106". You can easily rearrange the couch pieces to fit different spaces and needsWhether arranged in an L-shape or placed side by side, it effortlessly adapts to diverse needsfrom creating a snug reading nook to hosting movie nights with friends, enjoying laid-back family moments, or converting into a convenient sofa bed for guests. The sectional sofa's spacious design and modular construction makes moving and rearraning a piece of cake
      • No Assembly Required: Vesgantti cloud sofa arrives tool-free and vacuum-packed for effortless setup. Simply unbox, allow it to expand for up to 72 hours, and its ready to enjoy! Our boneless cloud couch can be placed on either side for customizable comfortstart relaxing from the moment you get it. Note: Minor wrinkles are normal after compression, and cushions may take up to three days to fully regain their fluffiness
      • Available in 6 Color Options: Two premium fabrics include plush corduroy couch and luxurious chenille couchboth offering exceptional comfort, lasting durability, and easy upkeep. These skin-friendly, pet-resistant materials withstand scratching while maintaining their softness, perfect for families with children and pets. For added convenience, the removable throw pillow covers and back cushion covers are machine-washable, effortlessly blending style with practicalityideal for anyone seeking a fresh, low-maintenance sectional couches for living room. The frame of the seating area is made by FSC-certified wood, safely use and environmentally friendly.
      • Space-Savvy Modular Comfort: Engineered for space-conscious living, this versatile fluffy sofa adapts seamlessly to any environmentfrom compact apartments to family rooms and small living spaces. Its innovative legless, minimalist design fits various decor styles, making it a versatile addition to different living spaces. For convenient delivery, the foam couch ships in two separate boxes (which may arrive at different times). Your satisfaction is guaranteedshould the product not meet your expectations, our dedicated customer service team will promptly provide a satisfactory resolution

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        Amazon Customer
        5 out of 5 stars
        Very comfortable sofa, fast rebound, overall satisfying purchase
        I bought this Vesgantti boneless couch with chaise on Amazon and overall we are very happy with it. The entire sofa came in just two large boxes which made the delivery and moving process much easier. I originally thought a sectional of this size would take many boxes but the packaging was very efficient. After unboxing, the memory foam started to rebound quickly. By the end of the first day it reached about eighty percent, and after two days it fully expanded and could be used normally. There was a slight factory smell when opening the packaging. It is normal for new corduroy furniture. I sprayed some fragrance on it and the smell was easily covered. The part I am less satisfied with is the pillows. Both the two small pillows and the three backrest cushions did not rebound very well. Even after fluffing them according to the instructions, they only recovered to about seventy percent and still look a bit flat. The workmanship of the sofa itself is impressive. The corduroy fabric feels soft, warm and very comfortable. My whole family loves it. The kids especially like the texture of the fabric and they keep saying it feels super cozy when sitting or laying on it. One thing to note is when the room temperature is warm and the AC is not on, the fabric can feel slightly hot. Also, the overall size of the sofa is a bit larger than I expected so make sure to measure your space. Overall, this sofa is comfortable, looks clean and modern, and the setup process is effortless. Worth the price.

        About this Item

        • Comfortable Support: Expertly engineered with a high-density foam and spring system that delivers the perfect balance of plush softness and supportive structurethe integrated spring system provides lasting resilience and extended durability, while the memory foam delivers a sensation of cloud-like comfort. Designed for ultimate relaxation, the generous 28" seat depth, elevated back cushion and arcuate armrests create an inviting lounging oasis, while the spacious 58" chaise lounge offers ample room to stretch out. Thoughtfully incorporated ergonomic features ensure ideal support for prolonged sitting or reclining
        • Fully Modular Design: This modular sofa offers ultimate flexibility with a total width of 106". You can easily rearrange the couch pieces to fit different spaces and needsWhether arranged in an L-shape or placed side by side, it effortlessly adapts to diverse needsfrom creating a snug reading nook to hosting movie nights with friends, enjoying laid-back family moments, or converting into a convenient sofa bed for guests. The sectional sofa's spacious design and modular construction makes moving and rearraning a piece of cake
        • No Assembly Required: Vesgantti cloud sofa arrives tool-free and vacuum-packed for effortless setup. Simply unbox, allow it to expand for up to 72 hours, and its ready to enjoy! Our boneless cloud couch can be placed on either side for customizable comfortstart relaxing from the moment you get it. Note: Minor wrinkles are normal after compression, and cushions may take up to three days to fully regain their fluffiness
        • Available in 6 Color Options: Two premium fabrics include plush corduroy couch and luxurious chenille couchboth offering exceptional comfort, lasting durability, and easy upkeep. These skin-friendly, pet-resistant materials withstand scratching while maintaining their softness, perfect for families with children and pets. For added convenience, the removable throw pillow covers and back cushion covers are machine-washable, effortlessly blending style with practicalityideal for anyone seeking a fresh, low-maintenance sectional couches for living room. The frame of the seating area is made by FSC-certified wood, safely use and environmentally friendly.
        • Space-Savvy Modular Comfort: Engineered for space-conscious living, this versatile fluffy sofa adapts seamlessly to any environmentfrom compact apartments to family rooms and small living spaces. Its innovative legless, minimalist design fits various decor styles, making it a versatile addition to different living spaces. For convenient delivery, the foam couch ships in two separate boxes (which may arrive at different times).
